name: The Dragon Bridge
description:
Inspired by the Dragon Bridge in Da nang Vietnam. This iconic landmark lights up the city skyline every Saturday and Sunday night with a fire and water show that everyone can enjoy. 
Animated by artist Chris Mcbride, viewable with Augmented Reality through the Eyejack app.
This artwork is part of the official selection for the Prosthetic Reality Volume 2 Book 
#PRV2 #EyeJack #Vietnam #Animation #Dragon
